# VMware ESXi Commands Reference

A comprehensive collection of essential VMware ESXi commands for administrators. This guide includes commands for managing ESXi hosts, virtual machines, storage, networking, and more.

---

Hereâ€™s a full list of the 100 VMware ESXi commands from the PDF, formatted in a clean and organized way for your GitHub repository. The commands are grouped by category and include descriptions and use cases.

